data.description: Absolutely pristine, this stunning 3-bed, 1.5-bath home in the desirable Briarfield neighborhood boasts a complete renovation. From gleaming newer cabinets to fresh flooring and paint, every corner exudes a brand-new allure. Not a soul has lived in it since its transformation, ensuring a truly fresh start. Plus, revel in the expansive yard and sizable shed, perfect for all your storage needs. Enjoy outdoor living on the spacious deck, making every moment at home a delight. Located near the Newport News Shipyard, Hampton Coliseum, Hampton High, Bluebird Gap Farm, Langley AFB, shopping, entertainment and so much more.
